# Module structure

All the Zera implementations contain this 5 files.
- Actions.pm
- API.pm
- Components.pm
- Controller.pm
- View.pm


###### /Zera/ModuleName/Actions.pm
This is the module to store the functions that do the work, update a database, exploit an API, work whit files, etc.
###### /Zera/ModuleName/API.pm
This is the module to store the API rest functions.
###### /Zera/ModuleName/Components.pm
This is the module to store the functions to display small special sections of a webpage.
###### /Zera/ModuleName/Controller.pm
This is the controller file where the special functions will be stored.
###### /Zera/ModuleName/View.pm
This is the module to store the functions to display a webpage.
